    Any different licensing scheme may be negotiated with the author(s).
 
INSTALLATION
    x2dot can be easily compiled and installed. See file "INSTALL" for
    instructions.
 
    x2dot can directly call Graphviz dot:
     * Graphviz Dot (http://www.graphviz.org/)

    If you want to make changes to the source code, you might need the following tools to regenerate the code:
     * Flex (http://flex.sourceforge.net)
     * Bison (http://www.gnu.org/software/bison)
     * Gengetopt (http://www.gnu.org/software/gengetopt)

